    "content": "<h1 id=\"resources-contribution\">Resources &amp; Contribution<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#resources-contribution\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h1>\n<p>This section covers how to use Chekameh, contribute to the project, and find related materials.</p>\n<h2 id=\"getting-started\">Getting Started<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#getting-started\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h2>\n<p>New to the site? Start here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"/en/guide/\">User Guide</a></strong> — Learn how to navigate the map, use the timeline, and explore poet profiles</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"/en/guide/faq/\">FAQ</a></strong> — Common questions answered</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"/en/guide/glossary/\">Glossary</a></strong> — Terms and concepts explained</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"contribute-data\">Contribute Data<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#contribute-data\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h2>\n<p>We welcome contributions from anyone with knowledge of Persian poetry or history.</p>\n<h3 id=\"adding-poets\">Adding Poets<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#adding-poets\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h3>\n<p>If you know of a poet who should be included:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Gather biographical info (birth/death dates, locations)</li>\n<li>List major works</li>\n<li>Note connections to other poets or literary movements</li>\n<li>Submit via GitHub or contact form</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"correcting-information\">Correcting Information<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#correcting-information\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h3>\n<p>Found an error? Let us know:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Wrong dates or locations</li>\n<li>Missing works</li>\n<li>Incorrect associations</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"cities-and-regions\">Cities and Regions<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#cities-and-regions\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h3>\n<p>Help us map historical cities to modern coordinates:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Provide historical names and variants</li>\n<li>Modern location (city, country, coordinates)</li>\n<li>Time periods of literary activity</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"contribute-code\">Contribute Code<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#contribute-code\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h2>\n<p>Developers can help improve the site itself:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix bugs</li>\n<li>Add features</li>\n<li>Improve performance</li>\n<li>Enhance accessibility</li>\n</ul>\n<p>See the <a href=\"https://github.com/MDaV05/PersianCultureMap\">GitHub repo</a> for issues and pull requests.</p>\n<h2 id=\"translation\">Translation<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#translation\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h2>\n<p>The site supports English and Persian. Help us improve translations:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Correct existing translations</li>\n<li>Add missing content in either language</li>\n<li>Suggest better terminology</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"resources\">Resources<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#resources\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"external-links\">External Links<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#external-links\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Academic databases on Persian poetry</li>\n<li>Digital archives of manuscripts</li>\n<li>Related projects and research</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"citation\">Citation<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#citation\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h3>\n<p>If you use Chekameh in academic work, please cite:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Chekameh: Persian Poetry Map. <a href=\"https://chekameh.xyz\">https://chekameh.xyz</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"license\">License<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#license\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Content: Open license (details TBD)</li>\n<li>Code: MIT License</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"contact\">Contact<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#contact\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h2>\n<p>Questions or suggestions? Reach out via:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>GitHub Issues</li>\n<li>Email (coming soon)</li>\n<li>Social media links</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p><em>Thanks to everyone who contributes. This project grows because of community support.</em></p>",
